OL,3,CHealth chiefs warn of impact of draft
OL,4,Cbudget
OL,6,FA body representing health leaders in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland has warned that the
OL,8,Fdraft budget could result in service
OL,9,Fcuts equivalent to the loss of 10,000
OL,10,Fhealth staff.
OL,12,FThe Northern Ireland Confederation for
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care said the budget
OL,14,Fproposals will require "high-impact
OL,15,Fcuts on a scale not previously seen".
OL,17,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt has
OL,18,Falready warned the draft budget could
OL,19,Fleave him facing a #400million funding
OL,20,Fshortfall.
