OL,3,CHealth chiefs warn of impact of draft
OL,4,Cbudget
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Confederation for
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care (Nicon), the
OL,8,Fmembership body representing the
OL,9,Fleaders of organisations in the
OL,10,Fsector, has made its submission to the
OL,11,Fpublic consultation over the spending
OL,12,Fplans.
OL,14,FIt said the proposed health budget is
OL,15,F"unworkable and counter strategic" and
OL,16,Fwould have "catastrophic impacts for
OL,17,Ffrontline services".
OL,19,FThe powersharing Executive at Stormont
OL,20,Fagreed a draft budget for 2025-26 in
OL,21,FDecember.
