OL,3,CHealth chiefs warn of impact of draft
OL,4,Cbudget
OL,6,FNeil Guckian, speaking on behalf of
OL,7,FNicon, said: "Our consultation
OL,8,Fresponse details how the HSC (health
OL,9,Fand social care) will need to find
OL,10,F#400 million savings in 2025-26.
OL,12,F"Coupled with the increase in demand
OL,13,Ffor health and social care services,
OL,14,Fthis is an untenable ask.
OL,16,F"Achieving this level of savings in-
OL,17,Fyear will require high-impact cuts on
OL,18,Fa scale not previously seen, with
OL,19,Fcatastrophic impacts for frontline
OL,20,Fservices.
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
