OL,3,CHealth chiefs warn of impact of draft
OL,4,Cbudget
OL,6,F"Even if the minister were to agree to
OL,7,Fimplement such measures, a one-year
OL,8,Fbudget means our senior teams will
OL,9,Flikely spend six months in statutory
OL,10,Fconsultation, leaving little to no
OL,11,Ftime to plausibly deliver this level
OL,12,Fof savings by the end of the financial
OL,13,Fyear."
OL,15,FLast week, the Stormont Executive
OL,16,Fpublished its programme for
OL,17,Fgovernment, which contained pledges of
OL,18,Fextra cash to tackle the hospital
OL,19,Fwaiting list crisis.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]
