OL,3,CHealth chiefs warn of impact of draft
OL,4,Cbudget
OL,6,FMr Guckian added: "Additionally,
OL,7,Falthough the Executive's plan for
OL,8,Fwaiting list investment is very
OL,9,Fwelcome, this funding must not be
OL,10,Fsecured by simply raiding the existing
OL,11,Fbudget for the day-to-day running of
OL,12,Fhealth and social care.
OL,14,F"This would be entirely counter-
OL,15,Fintuitive, as any investment in
OL,16,Fwaiting lists would be undermined by
OL,17,Fthe curtailment of services and cuts
OL,18,Felsewhere, such as domiciliary care
OL,19,Fpackages, leading to further backlogs
OL,20,Fin care.
OL,26,@nD@SOUvD@AOU
