OL,3,CHealth chiefs warn of impact of draft
OL,4,Cbudget
OL,6,F"We call on political leaders to
OL,7,Furgently agree a more rational,
OL,8,Finnovative approach to HSC funding
OL,9,Fthat will allow us time to implement
OL,10,Fthe strategic approach that we as
OL,11,Fleaders are confident we can deliver."
OL,13,FNicon said the proposed health funding
OL,14,Ffor Northern Ireland is at a 10-year
OL,15,Flow relative to NHS England.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@fO]
