OL,3,CHealth chiefs warn of impact of draft
OL,4,Cbudget
OL,6,FMr Guckian said: "While an innovative
OL,7,Ffinancial arrangement and financial
OL,8,Frecovery plan will help us through the
OL,9,Fnext three years, we must have a wider
OL,10,Fsocietal conversation about how health
OL,11,Fand care will have to adapt to meet
OL,12,Ffuture population needs sustainably.
OL,14,F"This will require bolder decision-
OL,15,Fmaking around additional revenue
OL,16,Fraising; moving care closer to
OL,17,Fcommunities; and prevention, including
OL,18,Fa rethink on how we support the public
OL,19,Fto take a more active role in their
OL,20,Fown health."
